# .gitignore for Spring Boot Backend

### Maven ###
target/
!.mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar
!**/src/main/**/target/
!**/src/test/**/target/

### STS ###
.apt_generated
.classpath
.factorypath
.project
.settings
.springBeans
.sts4-cache

### IntelliJ IDEA ###
.idea
*.iws
*.iml
*.ipr

### NetBeans ###
/nbproject/private/
/nbbuild/
/dist/
/nbdist/
/.nb-gradle/
build/
!**/src/main/**/build/
!**/src/test/**/build/

### VS Code ###
.vscode/

### Application ###
application-local.properties
application-prod.properties

### Logs ###
logs/
*.log

### File Uploads ###
uploads/

### OS ###
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

### Other ###
*.class
*.jar
*.war
*.ear
